	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				尽管我们这儿的天不总是蓝的吧，但窗户有趣一点不是啥坏事啊。
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p>
	来自阿根廷的建筑师 Aldana Ferrer Garcia 设计了这些折叠打开的窗户，一共三种，他为它们取了一个有幻想意义的名字“more sky”。&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
	“hopper niche”是最大众的一种，只有一个 15° 的倾斜，看上去像是将常年打开的窗户用玻璃固定起来，可以无顾忌地趴在上面。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/d78558866213.jpg" width="818" height="666" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/3d0ce75296de.jpg" width="818" height="924" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/efa40ce3ede2.jpg" width="818" height="673" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/7a4113f117f0.jpg" width="818" height="703" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	“awning niche”，看起来像将 3 个“hopper niche”反向叠加起来，与垂直墙面构成 45°，正好是一个做躺椅的空间，可以舒服地仰望天空。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/3c0968612fd6.jpg" width="818" height="658" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/ea6a651138ec.jpg" width="818" height="717" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/2636ffd88cad.jpg" width="818" height="563" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	"casement niche"像是将平开窗的空间用玻璃封闭起来，构成一个圆弧，可以直接坐在里面看书或者沉思，悬在半空时说不定能促进思考。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/b115aa460b9e.jpg" width="818" height="661" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/4057b89343ae.jpg" width="818" height="687" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	这组设计正在迪拜设计周上展示，它可以适应不同窗户的实际大小。<a href="http://aldanaferrergarcia.com/#/moresky/" target="_blank">这里是设计师的工作室。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/3986bc53a1ef.jpg" width="818" height="625" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/54cd6d5487d9.jpg" width="818" height="612" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/d982bed2c12e.jpg" width="818" height="780" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/9d8b15b531f0.jpg" width="881" height="679" title="手稿图" alt="手稿图" /><span>手稿图</span> 
</p>
<p>
	图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.designboom.com/design/dubai-design-week-global-grad-showaldana-ferrer-garcia-more-sky-10-31-2015/" target="_blank">designboom</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
		</div>
	</div>
